{"type": "article", "id": 16159, "title": "Beckett Simonon 新系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-16T06:50:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000855wSfavicltxTY1sjF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tBeckett Simonon 成立的目标是提供高品质有个性的鞋，以及可以接受的价格。他们新出的系列就仅仅使用两块正面革（full-grain leather）和未经加工的外底，配合尽可能少的剪裁，却能呈现毫不低价的效果，一共有黑、白、紫红三种颜色，<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/656797549/premium-shoes-for-the-new-breed-of-gentlemen\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143520S48mt05CvHoLGfl7.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143521epnKATZtqF1vVLDx.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143521fKD1L3JO5vPtXCGj.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261435221tY5WS0Hok2bGV7h.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}